This is a clean and easily customizable accordion plugin. You can customize your selectors and functionality. 

########## Setup ##########
1. Wrap your accordion content in an ".accordion" container.
2. Add ".title" to the element or container you want displayed when the accordion is collapsed.
3. Add ".content" to the container you want to be hidden when the accordion is collapsed.

########## Features ##########
1. If you want your content to function as an accordion in a mobile view only, use ".mobileAccordion" as the main container selector instead.
2. If you want all other accordions to collapse when you click on a new one, change the javascript setting "closeAll" to true.